@sec-distributed-training-systems-systems-distributed-training-fundamentals-97da (definition callout, line 214)
“with 30% of a step’s time spent on synchronization, the theoretical scaling ceiling is 1/0.30 ~ 3x”


Effective batch size = N x B x K_accum
