                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;div style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: {COLORS['TextSec']}; line-height: 1.6;"&gt;
                    &lt;strong&gt;Read:&lt;/strong&gt; @sec-[...] for the full derivation.&lt;br/&gt;
                    &lt;strong&gt;Build:&lt;/strong&gt; TinyTorch Module NN -- [what they will implement].
